description.ai-agent: The ILLA team and their users have customized various AI Agents that can address a range of scenarios, such as SEO, email generation, data analysis, and more. You can directly use these AI Agents or customize your own AI Agent to suit your specific needs.
description.app: The ILLA team and their users have created a wide range of AI-powered tools using ILLA Builder and ILLA AI Agent. These tools include customer data analysis systems, content generation and management systems, AI text generation, AI image generation, and more. You can directly try them out or fork them for your own team's use.
